Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:48.64,ED_cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be10}若是我在你面前出现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:50.60,ED_cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be10}就是“永远”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:54.22,ED_cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be10}无论喜欢 抑或讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:58.02,ED_cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be10}感情之前的是“绝对”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:14:05.46,ED_cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be10}24小时 望眼欲穿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:12.08,ED_cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be10}只想注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:16.42,ED_cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be10}宇宙规模的爱意I want you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:20.40,ED_cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be10}缠在你身边 全天候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:23.74,ED_cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be10}如果我做得好就Give me Chu？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:28.04,ED_cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be10}啊呀 不要傲娇Love me do
