Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:35.38,ED_cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be10}所谓希望就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:38.60,ED_cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be10}邂逅了心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.70,0:14:43.08,ED_cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be10}约好了要永远Be with you
